Introduction

SIOSIJAK (Korean: 시오시작; also stylized as SIO.SIJAK) is a performance girl group under Good Dream Entertainment. They made their music debut on March 12, 2018 with the digital single "Lalala". On October 1st, 2020, Yelim announced on her Instagram that the group would no longer be promoting, which was later also confirmed by Suna days later.
